title: Into the Woods and Weed Wackers (Barbara Alyn Woods as Deb Scott) • EP105
itunes:title: Into the Woods and Weed Wackers (Barbara Alyn Woods as Deb Scott) • EP105
description:
The phenomenal Barbara Alyn Woods (Deb Scott) is the ultimate Drama Queen.

 

She’s sharing not only her memories but her wisdom, her compassion and her strength with Hilarie, Sophia and Joy. Find out why a long lost relative in Wilmington helped her get the part.  Barbara's letting you in on everything Deb, Dan and Nathan.  


Plus, hot tub hair stories and why she doesn't have fond memories of those tan pants! 

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
